works.description: While the Ballerina Sweetspot chair is still in the production stages, Klutz Design has lately announced the availability of its second offering – the CanCans headphone stand. CanCans is a stylish and ergonomic headphone stand that makes a prominent place to keep your headphones. Done in solid wood and aluminum with high-gloss lacquer, Klutz Design’s CansCans stand holds both headphones and cables beautifully and safely in place. You can go for the all-white or all-black model with plain chrome knobs or choose one of the many colorful knobs.
